cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.IT 

The paper discusses the intersection of machine learning and wireless communication, specifically focusing on edge learning and radio resource management. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also touches upon system design and optimization, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
